					</span>
					<div class="flex mt-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
						<span class="bg-blue-50 w-3 rounded-full mr-2 "></span>
						<p class="w-3/5">Personalized Spatial Audio with dynamic head tracking places sound all around you </p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="shadow-md shadow-slate-100 h-12 flex justify-between items-center">
