						<div class="bg-[url('https://store.storeimages.cdn-apple.com/4668/as-images.apple.com/is/MME73?wid=2000&hei=2000&fmt=jpeg&qlt=95&.v=1632861342000')] bg-center bg-[length:100%_100%] w-48 h-48"></div>
